                     <p class="description font-s">Supports ongoing discovery, pre-clinical, and clinical studies research topics. These topics can be sourced from journal articles, industry reports, dissertation from leading research institutions, news release, and scientific technology brochures. Research topics help group information around particular scientific areas to give researchers access to detailed scientific material on a specific topic that can be used to further advance research. This provides researchers the ability to collaborate with their scientific peers on selected research topics and determine what publications are critical to meeting their R&amp;D objectives.
